	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b></b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />You have to take time into account.
<br />First you need to transform between NES cpu cycles and audio samples.  Use the clock cycle timestamps of each 4011 write to determine how long the byte would stay at that value.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


